name: Rubina Ashrafe
description: Well, I am looking for a true LOVE! I am a very sweet hearted woman. I am optimistic and nice, friendly and kind, romantic and funny! I’m very active, thoughtful and serious lady with loving heart and sincere soul, grace, elegance and passionate . I am a little bit old-fashioned, if we are talking about the family, and family values. I am interested in so many things, because nothing can be more exciting than this wonderful life!! I think I am a good person and will become a caring wife for a person who will choose me!
